    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193490/extras/c5dc47b33c83ad445d14a1d8c4676c95.avif?t=1763676459\" width=848 height=138 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Another One </strong>— a 1–8 player co-op extraction action with shooter elements. Dive into procedurally generated worlds full of random events and high-stakes challenges. Build your loadout and uncover the mystery before reality falls apart…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Will you and your team be able to survive in an environment where the world around you is falling apart?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193490/extras/da5c4bc332a73b1f549fbca7e757dd91.avif?t=1763676459\" width=900 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193490/extras/453cb82698f15e8fb321b43417de2545.webp?t=1763676459\" width=900 height=50 /></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Immerse yourself in a unique simulation where each entry into the game is a new, exciting story. Procedural generation creates liminal complexes, ensuring that no session will be like the previous one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193490/extras/3fdbd435f195258eb37dd625d2a570e4.avif?t=1763676459\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193490/extras/62ad4625516fe45d9ba5d67804fac906.webp?t=1763676459\" width=900 height=50 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The simulation is becoming more unstable by the moment. Electromagnetic storm burns out electronics, and the indigenous inhabitants of the simulations are becoming more aggressive. Your task is to have time to evacuate yourself and valuable resources before the simulation collapses. Experience the adrenaline and tension, where every decision you make may be your last!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193490/extras/d831bc8fc2f7b6e0a2a2b91f5e483cd1.avif?t=1763676459\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193490/extras/982e50507af800929b9e26ae538c7648.webp?t=1763676459\" width=900 height=50 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Every dive is a new challenge! Random item generation, entity behavior, and in-game events create a dynamic gaming environment where every choice matters. Prepare for unexpected scenario twists and unusual situations that will force you to adapt on the fly.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193490/extras/bc7164becb5d245c8d0efd8b0341c44e.avif?t=1763676459\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193490/extras/7b14fc85087a33f331ba4546af149347.webp?t=1763676459\" width=900 height=50 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Enjoy stunning graphics where powerful shadows and bright contrasts create an atmosphere of complete immersion. The interior of the complex makes you believe in its reality, and the stylistic post-process makes the game visually fascinating. Feel the real horror when every shadow suddenly comes to life!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193490/extras/44936c5c5249d25d9c5207cce6a9f802.avif?t=1763676459\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193490/extras/d498099661696361f44f93d58e26a097.webp?t=1763676459\" width=900 height=50 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Immerse yourself in the world of sound design, which will take you to the heart of what is happening. Deep sounds and powerful effects create an atmosphere that can cause goosebumps. Every rustle, every scream and rumble is a part of your adventure, the emotions of which you will not be able to forget!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193490/extras/83eccd0ebcec6b222949cfd942a04c67.avif?t=1763676459\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Screenshots and descriptions will be updated. Add Another one to your wishlist now to stay up to date with the latest news and updates!</strong></p>",
